{"tid":1963951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]將軍澳壇前黑警聚集，有散播病毒之風險。","createTime":"2020-04-08T12:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T02:31:00.000Z","uid":41292,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf6b6252a2e1bf390f82a34a424a679fb58b0b2","tid":1963951,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"[本壇討論]20:57<br />\n      五個月前，手足周子樂不幸因警暴離世。而因為武漢肺炎係香港擴散嘅原因，今日國民召集係網  上進行悼念。<br />\n    係將軍澳，一群防暴黑警以及狂化速龍聚集，以犯下殖民政府嘅禁令嘅做法黎進駐，情況有如軍隊入城，佢地針對年輕嘅國民黎紀錄個人資料，並且以佢地認為係攻擊性武器「大聲公」黎攻擊邨民。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWc6eX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWc6eX5.jpg&h=2e956ee5&s={SIZE}\" /> 來源:立場新聞<br />\n下圖為被黑警控告以「大聲公」襲擊黑警嘅無辜國民 <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s07eoRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs07eoRB.jpg&h=920bd905&s={SIZE}\" />  來源:蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n     係網上悼念結束後，黑警依然聚集係將軍澳一帶，包括寶林、坑口、將軍澳、調景嶺嘅殖民地鐵路部嘅站口同埋尚德、富康、廣明一帶，當中違反左殖民政府嘅聚集禁令，而近日有多宗黑警中招個案，令人擔心黑警嘅衛生同埋精神情況，可能會因為聚集而令到武漢肺炎喺黑警間大爆發，雖為喜事，但係驚黑警會好似之前個女黑警咁樣野到國民，所以我地建議黑警請減少聚集，降低散播病毒之風險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Er4DQyY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEr4DQyY.jpg&h=7b0df388&s={SIZE}\" /> 來源:立場新聞 <br />\n<br />\n我地提醒眾國民小心回家，而唔係個到住嘅國民就避免到一帶出沒。"},{"pid":"7817f051a01a1145e0dacbd2b9811399da42ef2f","tid":1963951,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"岩啦，病毒唔識分黃藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒死班9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a184f7da58e82b6406e1b315340babe0059379","tid":1963951,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9092df73b2dc997ee1cd3bbf7efb80e4771aa0b","tid":1963951,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"3月8號7個黑警圍住一個手足侮辱恐嚇 記唔記得佢? 好想條片做國際文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963948</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8924e5353ce0995c1f8c50ddac9e7ac6f6cd3ae","tid":1963951,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n下圖為被黑警控告以「大聲公」襲擊黑警嘅無辜國民 <br />\n 來源:<span style=\"color: red;\">香港電台</span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n無對稿，SOR"},{"pid":"d264ad1a911e02407e3c17bb9045dcce865aa914","tid":1963951,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"b54ce525e7568346074c5c0decec7bd85055200e","tid":1963951,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"依家根本唔會理有冇人出<br />\n總之有人經過就截住先 湊夠5人就罰得<br />\n<br />\n聽講仲兇人要即科現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c64b0eb41582565cb6837ec24604f1d205fe97","tid":1963951,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"死黑警縮返入狗竇啦"},{"pid":"0360a4371669251d40d12160567ad01a1da63e6a","tid":1963951,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b54ce525e7568346074c5c0decec7bd85055200e","tid":1963951,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"依家根本唔會理有冇人出<br />\n總之有人經過就截住先 湊夠5人就罰得<br />\n<br />\n聽講仲兇人要即科現金<img src=\"/